name: BabyoctopusDAO
description:
Baby octopus currently has its own contract destruction function to repurchase baby octopus tokens, and can automatically obtain BNB dividends for each transaction and transfer each transaction.LP can be automatically added to the pool to increase fluidity and pool thickness,BabyoctopusDAO can automatically burn, distribute dividends, and mint stable currency OUSD, similar to the Luna stable currency mode,
refund plan
No project can be 100% successful, including Baby octopus DAO.
If the project fails for any reason, the community will initiate a proposal, and if the vote is passed, a refund process will be initiated.
We will calculate the financing situation of the DAO at that time and the remaining amount of the treasury, and take a snapshot of the investment address at that time.
Everyone can get a fair refund, if the financing fails, an investment form will be posted on Twitter and we will check the address.
